title: The Real Housewives Of Miami S03E15 Reunion Part 1 WEB-DL x264-R
description:
The ladies of Miami reunite to set the record straight on some of the most talked about antics of the season. Joanna and Lisa's perfect friendship turns sour when Joanna goes below the belt by blaming Lisa's fertility issue on her partying lifestyle. Alexia struggles to see both sides of the couch, but doesn't hold anything back when Lisa questions Alexia's motives. While Adriana defends herself again and again on her secret marriage, Lea continues to break Adriana's olive branch.

Thanks to RKSTR for capping and sharing
